underlying_goal: Improve project documentation by ensuring all relevant experiment hyperparameters are documented.
primary_success: Performed a comprehensive gap analysis between code and documentation, presented a prioritized list of missing items, and then precisely updated the documentation based on user feedback.
brief_summary: The user wanted to update CLAUDE.md with relevant hyperparameters from classifier code. The agent analyzed the codebase, identified all undocumented hyperparameters, and presented a prioritized list to the user. Based on user selection, it then edited CLAUDE.md, adding the specified parameters to the reporting tables and creating a new section for less variable ones.
